### Organisation Details

registeredIsaManager.title = Is your organisation registered to manage ISAs with HMRC?
registeredIsaManager.heading = Is your organisation registered to manage ISAs with HMRC?
registeredIsaManager.error.required = You must select either yes or no.  For example select yes, if you are registered as an ISA manager with HMRC

zReferenceNumber.title = What is your organisation’s Z-reference number?
zReferenceNumber.heading = What is your organisation’s Z-reference number?
zReferenceNumber.details.summary = Don’t know your Z-reference number?
zReferenceNumber.details.content = If you’re already registered with HMRC as an ISA manager you can {0} if you have forgotten it or don’t know it.
zReferenceNumber.details.content.link = check your Z-reference number
zReferenceNumber.hint = This is a Z followed by 4 numbers, for example Z1234
zReferenceNumber.error.required = If you are a registered ISA Manager you must tell us your Z-reference number. This number is a Z followed by 4 numbers
zReferenceNumber.error.invalid = Z-reference number must only include a Z followed by 4 numbers
zReferenceNumber.error.tooShort = The Z-reference number you have given is too short. The number is a Z followed by 4 numbers
zReferenceNumber.error.tooLong = The Z-reference number you have given is too long. The number is a Z followed by 4 numbers

tradingUsingDifferentName.title = Does your organisation trade using a different name?
tradingUsingDifferentName.heading = Does your organisation trade using a different name?
tradingUsingDifferentName.checkYourAnswersLabel = Does your organisation trade using a different name?
tradingUsingDifferentName.error.required = You must select either yes or no. For example select yes, if your organisation trades using a different name
tradingUsingDifferentName.change.hidden = trading using different a name

tradingName.title = What is your organisation’s trading name?
tradingName.heading = What is your organisation’s trading name?
tradingName.checkYourAnswersLabel = tradingName
tradingName.error.required = You must tell us what your organisation’s trading name is
tradingName.change.hidden = trading name

firmReferenceNumber.title = Financial Conduct Authority (FCA) Firm Reference Number (FRN)
firmReferenceNumber.heading = Financial Conduct Authority (FCA) Firm Reference Number (FRN)
firmReferenceNumber.label = What is your organisation’s FCA, FRN?
firmReferenceNumber.p1 = The FCA, FRN is a unique identification number assigned to each financial organisation and is crucial for verifying the legitimacy and authorisation status of organisations operating in the financial sector.
firmReferenceNumber.p2 = The number is used to track and manage regulated financial organisations.
firmReferenceNumber.p3 = The FRN is commonly referred to as the FCA number.
firmReferenceNumber.p4 = If you’re already registered as an ISA manager with HMRC but have forgotten or can’t find your FCA number -
firmReferenceNumber.checkYourAnswersLabel = FCA number
firmReferenceNumber.error.required = You must enter your organisation’s FCA, FRN. This is a 6 or 7 digit number
firmReferenceNumber.error.pattern = The FCA, FRN must not include letters a to z, hyphens, spaces or apostrophes
firmReferenceNumber.error.incorrectLength = The FCA, FRN  must be a six or seven digit number
firmReferenceNumber.change.hidden = FCA number
firmReferenceNumber.hint = The FCA, FRN is usually a 6 or 7 digit number
firmReferenceNumber.link.text = you can check the ISA managers list to find your number

organisationTelephoneNumber.title = What is the telephone number of your organisation?
organisationTelephoneNumber.heading = What is the telephone number of your organisation?
organisationTelephoneNumber.hint = This number will only be used by HMRC to speak to ISA managers or liaison officers during the audit process
organisationTelephoneNumber.checkYourAnswersLabel = Organisation telephone number
organisationTelephoneNumber.error.required = Enter the phone number of your organisation. Use a UK phone number, like 01642 123 456 or 07777 777 777
organisationTelephoneNumber.error.tooLong = The phone number you have entered is too long. For example, a UK phone number, like 01642 123 456 or 07777 777 777
organisationTelephoneNumber.error.tooShort = The phone number you have entered is too short. Enter a UK phone number, like 01642 123 456 or 07777 777 777
organisationTelephoneNumber.error.invalid = The phone number must not include letters a to z, hyphens or apostrophes and must be a a UK phone number, like 01642 123 456 or 07777 777 777
organisationTelephoneNumber.change.hidden = organisation telephone number

registeredAddressCorrespondence.title = Do you want us to use the registered address to send you letters?
registeredAddressCorrespondence.heading = Do you want us to use the registered address to send you letters?
registeredAddressCorrespondence.error.required = Select yes if you want HMRC to use the address given for correspondence

