bvLockout.heading = The details you’ve entered do not match our records
bvLockout.p1 = Check your company’s Corporation Tax records and try again after 4 hours.
bvLockout.p2 = If you’re still having problems, contact the Corporation Tax helpline.
bvLockout.telephone = Telephone:
