bvLockout.p3 = Closed on weekends and bank holidays.

## Declaration
declarationForIsaManagers.title = Declaration for registering and enrolling ISA managers
declarationForIsaManagers.heading = Declaration for registering and enrolling ISA managers
declarationForIsaManagers.junior.li1 = I’m applying to manage Junior ISA accounts, I undertake to publicise (and update where appropriate) statements of the minimum amount that may be subscribed to a Junior ISA account on a single occasion, and the permitted means of payment on subscriptions
declarationForIsaManagers.junior.li2 = I’m applying to manage Junior ISA accounts, I undertake to inform persons proposing to make a subscription to a Junior ISA account (other than the named child) that the subscription is a gift to the child
declarationForIsaManagers.p1 = Do you agree to the following statements:
declarationForIsaManagers.li1 = the ISA products and investments will meet the qualifying criteria as described in the ISA regulations and ISA managers’ guidance
declarationForIsaManagers.li2 = the ISAs opened and subscriptions made under my management will comply with the ISA regulations
declarationForIsaManagers.li3 = all HMRC ISA returns and reporting obligations will be accurate and made in accordance with the ISA regulations and ISA managers’ guidance
declarationForIsaManagers.li4 = I’m not subject to any requirement or prohibition imposed by or under any rules made by the Financial Conduct Authority or the Prudential Regulation Authority under Part 4A of FISMA 2000 which would prevent me from acting as an account manager
declarationForIsaManagers.li5 = the information I’ve provided in this application is, to the best of my knowledge and belief, is correct and true
declarationForIsaManagers.li6 = I understand that if my circumstances change I’ll notify HM Revenue and Customs immediately
declarationForIsaManagers.p2 = By continuing, I confirm that I have understood all of the statements.
declarationForIsaManagers.action = I agree, submit

## Confirmation
confirmation.title = confirmation dummy
confirmation.heading = confirmation dummy
